body:
This PR is intended to simplify Umpire's smoke/stand-alone tests through the following initial changes:

- Remove attempts to test installations prior to v2.0.0, reporting them as 'Skipped';
- Reports tests as 'skipped' if the `bin` directory is not create (i.e., if the package is not installed with examples enabled, which is not the default).

@davidbeckingsale
